1
00:00:58,053 --> 00:01:01,029
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,029 --> 00:01:02,999
=Episode 3=

3
00:01:02,999 --> 00:01:07,021
(I am Your Third Sister-in-law Now)

4
00:02:29,159 --> 00:02:30,360
Is it time?

5
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:33,599
It's getting late, dear.
You should go to rest.

6
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:01,280
A beauty in the bath
is truly a sight to behold.

7
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:07,080
But the undergarment
is a nuisance in the medicinal bath.

8
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:12,520
Don't wear it next time.

9
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,840
Thanks for the reminder, dear.

10
00:03:33,088 --> 00:03:35,520
(Fufeng Pavilion)

11
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:43,840
Master, everything has been arranged.

12
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,039
Anything on his background?

13
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:51,719
He does have relatives in the capital
and debts at the Zuixian Building.

14
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:55,879
As you commanded,
I've investigated his former residence.

15
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:58,039
So last night,

16
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:00,199
it wasn't him?

17
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,800
What about Master Zhaoxi?

18
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,280
Still no news.

19
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,000
Who's back?

20
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,839
It's Miss Xuanji.

21
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:20,519
She returned partly
for your wedding with Master Zhaoxi,

22
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:23,639
and partly for the new tavern's opening.

23
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:29,079
The Xuanji Pavilion serves the court.
Still, the Gu family should bear in mind

24
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:32,319
that their extensive family business
invites trouble.

25
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,360
Master.

26
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:39,720
Our intelligence network operates
in both plain sight and the shadows.

27
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:44,079
We pride ourselves on being
the top intelligence organization.

28
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:46,759
Yet we can't even track down
our own young master.

29
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:50,680
Is he truly untraceable?

30
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:55,120
Or is someone in the Gu family
obstructing us?

31
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,160
I can't tell.

32
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,199
Keep investigating.

33
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:04,639
Yes.

34
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:13,519
(Am I doing the right thing or not?)

35
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:23,240
Take the medicine.

36
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:23,879
Alright.

37
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,600
Be patient. We'll be next.

38
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,680
Thank you.

39
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:29,240
Thank you.

40
00:05:30,439 --> 00:05:34,360
Master Zhaoxi and you are kind people.
Heaven blesses him.

41
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:37,720
Yeah, you two share deep affection.

42
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:39,879
Master Zhaoxi will return safely.

43
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:42,040
Yeah, he'll surely return.

44
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:44,519
Since Master Zhaoxi
took over the pharmacy,

45
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,639
he's given us
free consultations every month.

46
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:50,560
We're all deeply grateful
for his kindness.

47
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:51,560
Yeah.

48
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:56,160
Don't mention it.
We're just doing what's right.

49
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:59,600
But if you hear any news of Zhaoxi,

50
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,399
please inform us immediately.

51
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,879
- We will.
- Rest assured.

52
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:04,399
We definitely will. Let's go.

53
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:12,959
Still worried about Zhaoxi?

54
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:18,879
I heard your father flew into a rage
and threw a teacup at you.

55
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,240
You jest, Your Highness.

56
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,680
(Prince Rui, Yin Huan)
Don't call me that.

57
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,319
I'd rather enjoy tea and wine

58
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:29,199
while traveling and playing chess
than being a so-called "Your Highness".

59
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,959
Though I pity your sister-in-law.

60
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:42,920
What a beauty, newly wed yet left alone.

61
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:48,600
I hope she truly shares the deep bond
with Zhaoxi as she claims.

62
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,120
Thank you.

63
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:09,439
Master.

64
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:18,399
What happened, Chaosheng?

65
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:20,759
My heaven-blessed third brother

66
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,000
has returned.

67
00:07:30,112 --> 00:07:33,165
(Fufeng Pavilion)

68
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,319
Step aside.

69
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,560
You're no match for me.

70
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,079
We serve different masters.

71
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,160
(Zhe Zhu, Earth Unit of Xuanji Pavilion)
You should know

72
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:43,360
we must attempt our master's orders
even when impossible.

73
00:07:45,439 --> 00:07:46,480
What is going on?

74
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:51,360
My third brother returned injured.
Can't I even visit him?

75
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,879
The family head says

76
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:57,480
that no visitors are allowed
until Master Zhaoxi is out of danger.

77
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,360
Let's go.

78
00:08:13,439 --> 00:08:15,399
Dear, what do you think
of our eldest brother?

79
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:21,120
It seems Master Chaosheng
and Master Zhaoxi aren't so close.

80
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,800
He set up a memorial
while Master Zhaoxi was missing,

81
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,800
declaring him dead to all.

82
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:31,240
Now hearing of his return,
Master Chaosheng grows restless.

83
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,679
If you were the murderer

84
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:36,320
and learned your victim survived,

85
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,799
what would you do first?

86
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:44,360
Check on the survivor, naturally.

87
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,679
And inspect the body.

88
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:57,200
Are you saying
that Master Chaosheng is the murderer?

89
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:02,159
My husband is alive.
What do you mean by "murderer"?

90
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:10,600
Let's go. To become Gu Zhaoxi,
you have much to learn.

91
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,519
Chaosheng has been quite low-key lately.

92
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,360
You're recovering well.

93
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:40,240
But I just recalled
that Zhaoxi has an old scar.

94
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,399
To avoid suspicion,

95
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:46,039
I need your cooperation.

96
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:53,080
My lady.

97
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,519
You never said

98
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:57,879
I had to do this to be your "husband".

99
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,159
Weren't you calling me "dear" yesterday?

100
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:04,440
Why are you calling me "my lady" now?

101
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:07,600
I will spare no effort
to repay your kindness, my lady.

102
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:10,799
But my physical form
is a gift from my parents.

103
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:13,840
I'd rather not forge this wound.

104
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:28,000
The shape of his eyebrow
is somewhat softer than yours.

105
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:31,919
There's a tear mole
at the corner of his eye.

106
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,240
Do I resemble him?

107
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,679
Master, you have a visitor
in the front hall.

108
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:01,320
Didn't the family head say
that we receive no visitors these days?

109
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:06,000
Yes, but it's Master Wenshuang.

110
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:28,879
Wenshuang.

111
00:11:31,648 --> 00:11:35,104
(Gu Wenshuang,
fourth young master of the Gu family)

112
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:43,279
Luckily I made it in time.
Today is the Lantern Festival.

113
00:11:43,639 --> 00:11:46,000
The glass lanterns
have been trendy in Mobei lately.

114
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:50,720
I know you dislike darkness,
so I put these in your courtyard.

115
00:11:51,639 --> 00:11:54,039
How's the investigation going? Any news?

116
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:59,279
I've been gone for so long,
and you only care about the tips?

117
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,639
It's not like that.

118
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:06,399
I'm teasing you. Don't be so tense.

119
00:12:07,279 --> 00:12:10,480
I heard that Physician Qin
roams the world.

120
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:11,720
He's no longer in Mobei.

121
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:16,240
And no one knows where he is.

122
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:19,840
But that hardly troubles me.

123
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:23,960
I've asked around.
He is in the capital right now.

124
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,879
But Yuluo, you must tell me

125
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,720
why you are looking for him.

126
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:31,480
For Zhaoxi, naturally.

127
00:12:32,039 --> 00:12:32,840
Zhaoxi?

128
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,120
Didn't he...

129
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:41,000
I heard that Chaosheng
has arranged his funeral affairs.

130
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:44,919
Yuluo, you never married Zhaoxi.

131
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:48,159
You should try to let him go.

132
00:12:52,879 --> 00:12:54,200
Who says Zhaoxi is dead?

133
00:12:56,399 --> 00:12:59,440
You just returned, so you may not know
that he has come back.

134
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,039
What?

135
00:13:02,759 --> 00:13:07,440
But he was wounded by bandits
and needs to recover.

136
00:13:08,559 --> 00:13:12,519
But you just said
that Physician Qin is in the capital.

137
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:16,960
Yuluo, do you truly love Zhaoxi?

138
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,600
Do you truly intend to marry him?

139
00:13:20,559 --> 00:13:23,240
If you're reluctant, I can help you...

140
00:13:27,639 --> 00:13:31,000
Days ago, we completed the rites
before the entire Gu family.

141
00:13:32,759 --> 00:13:35,639
I am your third sister-in-law now.

142
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,759
But you two...

143
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:03,879
Why did you...

144
00:14:04,519 --> 00:14:05,679
I woke up, but you were gone.

145
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:24,679
The night wind chills.
Don't catch a cold.

146
00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:31,440
Zhaoxi.

147
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:46,480
He's not well. I'll take him back first.

148
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:50,039
You've traveled a long way. Rest early.

149
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:54,759
Yuluo, it's the Lantern Festival.
Shall we go see the river lanterns?

150
00:14:57,159 --> 00:14:59,480
The streets are full of people.

151
00:14:59,799 --> 00:15:02,039
You will surely find
who you've been looking for.

152
00:15:11,159 --> 00:15:13,360
Xuan Qing, I'm going out.

153
00:15:13,399 --> 00:15:15,240
Master, shall I accompany you?

154
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,360
While I'm away,

155
00:15:17,039 --> 00:15:19,639
my "husband" might need tending.

156
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,279
Stay.

157
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:26,039
Wherever he goes, don't interfere.
Just follow in secret.

158
00:15:28,159 --> 00:15:29,440
Don't let him find out.

159
00:15:30,159 --> 00:15:30,960
Yes.

160
00:15:42,679 --> 00:15:45,440
- Nice!
- Wonderful!

161
00:15:45,759 --> 00:15:46,720
So beautiful.

162
00:15:49,914 --> 00:15:50,782
Nice!

163
00:16:03,799 --> 00:16:06,600
Zhaoxi's health has truly declined.

164
00:16:07,279 --> 00:16:09,960
I hope Physician Qin
can cure his chronic ailment.

165
00:16:15,279 --> 00:16:17,279
When did he come back?

166
00:16:18,799 --> 00:16:19,600
Two days ago.

167
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:36,360
- Nice!
- Great!

168
00:16:41,639 --> 00:16:42,720
- Nice!
- Great!

169
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:48,720
The Lantern Festival
concludes with molten iron fireworks.

170
00:16:49,399 --> 00:16:50,519
You'll love it.

171
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:54,279
Is Physician Qin truly here?

172
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:10,079
I've been away for so long.
Won't you even welcome me back?

173
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:22,559
Can you tell me now?

174
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:27,160
Physician Qin had an old acquaintance.

175
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,160
The owner of Zuixian Building.

176
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,039
She rarely shows up.

177
00:17:31,119 --> 00:17:33,960
Only on Lantern Festival
does she make her appearance.

178
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:37,279
Each year, Physician Qin
returns to the capital

179
00:17:37,759 --> 00:17:39,359
to see her from afar.

180
00:17:41,279 --> 00:17:44,640
Physician Qin is quite a devoted person.

181
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,000
Oh, right.

182
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:05,079
I obtained this at the temple
for peace and prosperity.

183
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:07,960
It's potent. Do you like it?

184
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:13,440
I brought this back from Mobei.

185
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:17,119
I severed your bracelet by mistake
at Xuanji Pavilion.

186
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,000
You lost.

187
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,480
Wait.

188
00:18:25,799 --> 00:18:26,759
Your bracelet...

189
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:28,599
It's yours.

190
00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:48,200
Since then, I've wanted
to get you a new one.

191
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:16,720
I hate to be in debt.

192
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:31,640
- Nice!
- Great!

193
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:42,039
- Nice!
- Great!

194
00:20:23,525 --> 00:20:28,588
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

195
00:20:29,125 --> 00:20:34,446
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

196
00:20:35,013 --> 00:20:41,641
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

197
00:20:41,641 --> 00:20:46,405
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

198
00:20:46,405 --> 00:20:48,741
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

199
00:20:48,741 --> 00:20:55,441
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

200
00:20:55,441 --> 00:21:02,213
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

201
00:21:02,213 --> 00:21:09,349
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

202
00:21:09,349 --> 00:21:13,733
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

203
00:21:13,733 --> 00:21:16,357
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

204
00:21:16,357 --> 00:21:22,991
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

205
00:21:22,991 --> 00:21:29,541
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

206
00:21:29,541 --> 00:21:36,665
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

207
00:21:36,755 --> 00:21:41,125
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

208
00:21:41,125 --> 00:21:43,833
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

209
00:21:43,833 --> 00:21:49,733
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

210
